'''Ellen''' is a patient who came to see Pete after he got a cellulite-reducing machine.

==History==
Ellen came to see Pete after he got a cellulite-reducing machine. He used the machine on her and advised her that to see real results, she'd need to continue diet and exercise. She said it'd be easier just to come back in every day.
